    "body": "The aim for the official integrations in starship has been to offer basic integration with the shell, including forwarding the last status, pipestatus, job count and command duration. Beyond that some changes to the rust files are also necessary. \n\nRequests for POSIX-shell and other ksh variants have also been made in #928,  #3645 and #4628. ",
